name: Mei (Overwatch) LORA
description:
My sixth Overwatch LORA. Mainly focused on original appearance + a little bit of Lunar.

  • Original - back to being a bit more modular this time around - mei, brown eyes, hair bun, hair stick, glasses. Whatever you drop won't appear, so changing hairstyles and removing glasses shouldn't be a problem. For original armor - fur coat, fur-trimmed coat, fur footwear.

  • Lunar - mei, meilunar, dress, hair bun, hair stick

Checked strength range is 0.6-0.8. Strength 1 also felt stable enough, so feel free to experiment.

This time around issue were glasses - they interfered with burning in eyes quite a bit, so you gotta prompt for original brown color.

If you liked my work, you can donate here.

Review and comment with your experiences, I would appreciate whatever feedback you can provide in order to continue improving my technique.

Trained on Anything V4.5 with anime.vae.pt.

Samples are 512x768, without HighRes.fix, using OrangeCocoa 50/50 Mix , with OrangeMix VAE, and using EasyNegative embedding, CLIP Skip 2. Inpaint examples are txt2img with 1 single inpaint done on face (I will comment on exceptions).
